# Images Folder

Place the following images in this folder:

1. **favicon.png** (32x32 or 64x64 px)
   - Browser tab icon
   - Simple logo or icon representing Product Matcher

2. **og-image.png** (1200x630 px)
   - Social media preview image (Open Graph)
   - Should include app name, tagline, and visual
   - Used when sharing links on Twitter, Facebook, LinkedIn

3. **screenshot-upload.png** (recommended: 1200x800 px)
   - Screenshot of the upload interface
   - Show drag-and-drop functionality
   - Include folder upload and CSV metadata features

4. **screenshot-results.png** (recommended: 1200x800 px)
   - Screenshot of the results view
   - Show matched products with similarity scores
   - Include color-coded scores and grid layout

## Tips for Screenshots

- Use high-quality, clear images
- Show the app with sample data (use placeholder products)
- Ensure UI elements are readable
- Use consistent styling
- Optimize images for web (compress without losing quality)
- Consider using tools like TinyPNG or ImageOptim

